<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4804911>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Bidentogon californicus Buckett & Gardner. 1. Head and anterior rings, dorsal view. 2. Midbody ring, dorsal view. 3. Epiproct, lateral view. 4. Anterior end of male, ventral view. 5. Gonopods in situ, ventral view. 6. Gonopod tips, ventral view. Abbreviations: sm, solenomere; tz, terminal zone. SEM stub WS33-8." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4804911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4804921>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–12. Bidentogon expansus Shelley 7. Collum and first ring, dorsal view 8. Midbody ring, dorsal view. 9, Epiproct, dorsal view. 10. Gonopods in situ, ventral view. 11. Right leg 3, ventral view. 12. Part of right gonopod, ventral view.Abbreviations: ac, acropodite; f3, femur of third leg; pf, prefemorite; sm, solenomere; tz, terminal zone. SEM stub WS33-7." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4804921/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4804923>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–16. Bidentogon buttensis, n. sp. 13. Head and anterior rings, dorsal view. 14. Midbody ring, dorsal view. 15. Gonopods in situ, ventral view. 16. Gonopod tips, ventral view. Abbreviations: ac, acropodite; pf, prefemorite; sm, solenomere; tz, terminal zone. SEM stub WS33-9." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4804923/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4804929>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–20. Bidentogon norcal, n. sp. 17. Midbody ring, dorsal view. 18. Rght gonopod, lateral view. 19. Left gonopod, mesal view. 20. Detail of left gonopod, mesal view. SEM stub WS33-10. Abbreviations: sm, solenomere; tz, terminal zone." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4804929/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

